{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Decomposed into 4 child stories (addresses the G5/overflow decomposition findings): WS1 odd-cocoa-chase (80c3) migrate drift-refresh onto the workflow engine + delete bespoke _run_passes/pass2_verify/verifier_cfg behind a parity gate; WS2 gawky-koi-grain (bc6e) per-step verifier model: key (Sonnet downgrade) surfaced in the visual editor UX + BPMN round-trip/back-compat; WS3 tangly-shunt-scoop (4a0e) principled token-based chunking (depends_on WS1+WS2); WS4 crimp-polar-jag (679b) gate coach_notes on surviving>0. WS1/WS2/WS4 are unblocked; WS3 is blocked until WS1+WS2 close. Each child passes clarity_check + check_ac and carries file_impact. Per protocol, plan-review each child before claiming it."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782581501546474001,"uuid":"1b8a0f93-d640-4d75-8a69-5859f664b2cb"}